LINE.Text: The Purple Pound refers to the spending power of disabled households. A disabled household, is a household in which at least one of
the members has a disability. Organisations are missing out on the business of disabled consumers due to poor accessibility (both
physical and digital) and not being disability confident in their customer services approach.
